reviews.review_text:
Wonderful show this was my first show. I was stationed at Bethesda Naval Hospital at the time. 

I was blown away. I heard about the make a wish fella and the Ripple request years later. Up to that point I always thought that was the boys welcome to the family to me. LOL. Everyone cried when they pulled out Ripple. It was beautiful. Such an awesome show.
